Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:51.83,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,好 馬特烏和芷依塔去求見哈爾特根公王 探探情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:55.47,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,我和薇薇裝成參加者 混入大會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.22,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,李奧納多去查查參加者的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:03.25,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Aida, fual, alluel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.68,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,顯現吧 包裹隱藏之物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.85,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,<隐蔽者>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.86,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,OK 完美的隱蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:18.84,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,格倫森城 城牆 極其高大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.11,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,潛入 困難？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:23.20,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,是啊 只能正面上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.41,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,參加武藝大會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.54,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,我也可以參加吧
