Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.68,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 然後 找機會逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.15,Default,Navi,0,0,0,,盡早 需要調查遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.44,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 妮娃 聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.49,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,聰明？預料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.20,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,妮娃 謙虛
