Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:04.22,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,喂喂 這些傢伙可是來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.56,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,你太溫柔了 尼克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.45,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,這怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.39,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,根本不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.62,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,合格了
