Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:31.54,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:35.42,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不好意思 我們要參加武藝大會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:42.88,Default,Both,0,0,0,,去哪了
